flowchart TD
    Start([User Opens Dashboard]) --> Connect{Backend Connected?}
    Connect -- No --> Error[Show Connection Error]
    Connect -- Yes --> Settings[Select Network Interface]

    Settings --> StartSniff[Click 'Start Monitoring']
    StartSniff --> Loading[Backend initializes Scapy & ML Model]
    
    Loading --> LiveView[Live Dashboard View]
    
    subgraph "The Classification Loop"
        LiveView --> Wait[Wait for WebSocket Event]
        Wait --> NewData{New Prediction Received?}
        NewData -- Yes --> UpdateUI[Update Pie Chart & Event Log]
        UpdateUI --> Wait
    end

    LiveView --> Inspect[Click Flow in Table for Details]
    Inspect --> Modal[Show 54-Feature Statistics]
    
    LiveView --> Stop[Click 'Stop Monitoring']
    Stop --> Summary[Show Session Summary Report]
    Summary --> End([End Session])